comments.undefined: The application domain of the BMO is the bridge maintenance field. The BMO is designed to improve the management of maintenance knowledge of bridge lifecycle, and to provide more valuable information for bridge engineers to make holistic decisions.

comment.undefined: This bridge is a cable-stayed bridge with 540m (140m+260m+140m) long located in Dalian, Liaoning Province. Its main beam is connected with the pier and tower in the form of consolidation.
